(34, 3, 1171, 'Sekolah Dasar Islam Karakter (SDIK) Imam An-Nawawi Aceh', 3000000, 300000, NULL, 'Jl. Pari No 9 Lampriet Banda Aceh', '5.56673650', '95.33411410', 'https://goo.gl/maps/uiVJufyMsjhiw8ya9', NULL, 'sdik.an-nawawi.sch.id', '+6281282098961', '0852 6038 3593', NULL, 'sdik.ian', NULL, NULL, 'Admin', '+6281282098961', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '<header class=\"entry-header\" style=\"color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Merriweather, Georgia, serif;\"><h1 class=\"entry-title\" style=\"border: 0px; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 1.5; font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 3rem; font-style: inherit; font-weight: inherit; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; clear: both;\"><strong style=\"font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-size: 1rem; border: 0px; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-weight: bold; margin: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\">A. Sekilas Pandang Sekolah SIK-IAN Aceh</strong><br></h1></header><div class=\"entry-content\" style=\"border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: Merriweather, Georgia, serif; margin: 1.5rem 0px 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(68, 68, 68);\"><p style=\"border: 0px; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 1.5; font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-weight: inherit; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; margin-left: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\">Sekolah Islam Karakter (SIK) Imam An-Nawawi Aceh diselenggarakan di bawah Yayasan Al-Islam Aceh. Didirikan dengan tujuan untuk mendidik dan membina putra/putri kaum muslimin untuk menjadi generasi qur’ani, mandiri dan menjadi teladan kebaikan berdasarkan Al-Qur’an dan As-Sunnah dengan pemahaman salaf kepada masyarakat.</p><p style=\"border: 0px; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 1.5; font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-weight: inherit; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; margin-left: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\"><strong style=\"border: 0px; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-weight: bold; margin: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\">B. Visi, Misi dan Gambaran Kompetensi</strong><br><strong style=\"border: 0px; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-weight: bold; margin: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\"><em style=\"border: 0px; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-weight: inherit; margin: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\">Visi:</em></strong><br>Mewujudkan generasi Islam yang Rabbani, Qur’ani, dan Mandiri dengan mengikuti jejak salafus shalih.</p><p style=\"border: 0px; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 1.5; font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-weight: inherit; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; margin-left: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\"><strong style=\"border: 0px; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-weight: bold; margin: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\"><em style=\"border: 0px; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-weight: inherit; margin: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\">Misi:</em></strong></p><ol style=\"border: 0px; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-weight: inherit; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 30px; margin-left: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 35px; vertical-align: baseline; list-style-position: initial; list-style-image: initial;\"><li style=\"border: 0px; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-weight: inherit; margin: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\">Mewujudkan pendidikan yang berdasarkan Al-Qur’an dan Hadits dengan pemahaman para salafus shaleh.</li><li style=\"border: 0px; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-weight: inherit; margin: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\">Membina generasi Islam yang hafal Al-Qur’an dan mencintai Sunnah Nabi.</li><li style=\"border: 0px; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-weight: inherit; margin: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\">Menjadi lembaga sosial keagamaan yang mampu melahirkan masyarakat Muslim yang memiliki akhlak mulia dan bisa menjadi pemimpin umat.</li><li style=\"border: 0px; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-weight: inherit; margin: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\">Menyelenggarakan pendidikan Islam yang unggul tidak hanya dari sisi agama tapi juga ilmu pengetahuan sehingga lahir generasi yang kuat dan mandiri.</li></ol><p style=\"border: 0px; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 1.5; font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-weight: inherit; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; margin-left: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\"><strong style=\"border: 0px; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-weight: bold; margin: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\">Gambaran Kompetensi:</strong></p><p style=\"border: 0px; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 1.5; font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-weight: inherit; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; margin-left: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\"><strong style=\"border: 0px; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-weight: bold; margin: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\"><em style=\"border: 0px; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-weight: inherit; margin: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\">Aspek Qur’an</em></strong></p><ol style=\"border: 0px; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-weight: inherit; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 30px; margin-left: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 35px; vertical-align: baseline; list-style-position: initial; list-style-image: initial;\"><li style=\"border: 0px; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-weight: inherit; margin: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\">Mampu baca Qur’an terbata-bata di jenjang TK dan tuntas baca Qur’an dengan tajwid di kelas 1 jenjang SD.</li><li style=\"border: 0px; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-weight: inherit; margin: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\">Menghafal mandiri mulai kelas 2 jenjang SD, 1/2 hal per hari sd 1 hal per hari dan konsisten menghafal 1 hal per hari di jenjang SMP.</li><li style=\"border: 0px; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-weight: inherit; margin: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\">Memiliki hafalan dengan itqan.</li></ol><p style=\"border: 0px; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 1.5; font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-weight: inherit; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; margin-left: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\"><strong style=\"border: 0px; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-weight: bold; margin: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\"><em style=\"border: 0px; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-weight: inherit; margin: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\">Aspek B. Arab</em></strong></p><ol style=\"border: 0px; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-weight: inherit; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 30px; margin-left: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 35px; vertical-align: baseline; list-style-position: initial; list-style-image: initial;\"><li style=\"border: 0px; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-weight: inherit; margin: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\">Menguasai percakapan dasar harian Bahasa Arab di jenjang SD dan percakapan aktif di jenjang SMP.</li><li style=\"border: 0px; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-weight: inherit; margin: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\">Mampu menulis Arab dasar di jenjang SD dan menulis sesuai kaidah di jenjang SMP.</li><li style=\"border: 0px; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-weight: inherit; margin: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\">Menguasai kaidah nahwu dasar di jenjang SD dan kaidah nahwu/shorf di jenjang SMP.</li></ol><p style=\"border: 0px; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 1.5; font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-weight: inherit; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; margin-left: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\"><strong style=\"border: 0px; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-weight: bold; margin: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\"><em style=\"border: 0px; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-weight: inherit; margin: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\">Aspek Karakter</em></strong></p><ol style=\"border: 0px; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-weight: inherit; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 30px; margin-left: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 35px; vertical-align: baseline; list-style-position: initial; list-style-image: initial;\"><li style=\"border: 0px; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-weight: inherit; margin: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\">Memahami nilai-nilai adab yang digali dari ilmu diniyah sebagaimana dipahami salafus shalih.</li><li style=\"border: 0px; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-weight: inherit; margin: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\">Tumbuhnya perilaku adab yang baik mulai dari jenjang TK dan SD.</li><li style=\"border: 0px; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-weight: inherit; margin: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\">Membudaya dan konsistennya perilaku adab yang baik dari jenjang TK hingga SMP.</li></ol><p style=\"border: 0px; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 1.5; font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-weight: inherit; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; margin-left: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\"><strong style=\"border: 0px; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-weight: bold; margin: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\"><em style=\"border: 0px; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-weight: inherit; margin: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\">Aspek Akademik</em></strong></p><p style=\"border: 0px; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 1.5; font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-weight: inherit; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; margin-left: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\">Menguasai dan memahami materi mata pelajaran sesuai kurikulum yang berlaku.</p><p style=\"border: 0px; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 1.5; font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-weight: inherit; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; margin-left: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\"><strong style=\"border: 0px; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-weight: bold; margin: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\">C. Program Pendidikan Unggulan</strong></p><ol style=\"border: 0px; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inh